    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Polyurethane-90 is a urethane polymer formed by a multi-step process. First, a polyester is made by reacting Hexanediol, methylpentanediol and Diethyl Carbonate. A mixture of this polyester and Neopentyl Glycol is reacted with Isophorone Diisocyanate. The resulting polymer is Capped with HEMA."
